Prerequistes for vidoo processing with openCV 
==============================================

install libgtk2.x-dev for GUI functions.
install ffmpeg to be able to load video files:

sudo add-apt-repository ppa:mc3man/trusty-media
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get dist-upgrade
sudo apt-get install ffmpeg

Build opencv
==============
cmake .
make 
make install

Linking with opencv
====================
	g++ main.cpp `pkg-config opencv --cflags --libs` -o main

